HEADWORD: Deferment
<hw>De*fer"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 1st
<er>Defer</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of delaying; postponement.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My grief, joined with the instant business,⟦br⟧
